title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-09-2013 MON
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show DEC-09-2013 MON




Monday, December 09, 2013
Belleview-University Intersection Update

 
 

 - 9AM hour

1. Belleview Ave. intersection construction project is sped up after

 Gov. Hickenlooper's intervention. 

2. A look at Charles Krauthammer's remarks on the Senate change in the filibuster rule
     and change made by Obama by executive fiat.



 - 10AM hour

Money Monday with financial expert, Jordan Goodman.




 - 11AM hour

Mike talks about the possibility of a wealth tax and what it would mean.
